### Submit a new application (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/psacms/api/applications/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicantId": 1,
  "title": "2026 Canadian Youth Entrepreneurship Grant",
  "description": "This is a comprehensive business plan submitted for the entrepreneurship funding program. It includes market analysis, financial projections, and the proposed impact on the local economy."
}

### Fetch application pending review (Officer Perspective)
GET http://localhost:8080/psacms/api/applications/status/SUBMITTED
Accept: application/json